{"tid":157500,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（長文）男人冇銀 女人唔愛？","createTime":"2017-03-15T14:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T06:22:29.000Z","uid":91107,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13e4f956c73888e014ec0af6ecc4e2db295cc666","tid":157500,"uid":91107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:26:43.000Z","msg":"條女比帽我帶 綠帽唔怕帶最緊要除得快<br />\n忍心迫自己死心<br />\n<br />\n自問自己都算係好仔 陽光正常樣 170<br />\n又唔蒲又唔偷食又唔賭又唔飲酒<br />\n月入2皮幾野 政府工 結婚又有宿舍（現齡21歲）<br />\n<br />\n我都唔撚明 點解要簡個蒲精30幾歲中坑<br />\n每逢週末都老蘭，係有啲錢揸波子 <br />\n但係好明顯係貪你年青有樣有波食完鬆（model黎 相信咁多個巴打應該有係電視機見過佢） <br />\n我都唔明點解可以中個頭埋去 有錢係咪可以買到感情 <br />\n愈靚女就愈古惑 <br />\n<br />\n我對香港女仔好撚失望 <br />\n我以前冇諗過呢啲事會發生係我身上 以為呢啲女仔係佔小數 依家女人真係好9古惑<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢個香港唔睇錢嘅女仔係咪死撚晒"},{"pid":"be98199cbf8dd0e39dcd9b94a954b539ada7d697","tid":157500,"uid":91107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:31:50.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？"},{"pid":"a5859b99ded0afff38636cca023b429a2ff69076","tid":157500,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"戴"},{"pid":"c1a41f367033a2ea52e9dcd1ba5ef83c603e6f86","tid":157500,"uid":91107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n7撚到爆"},{"pid":"0a492911fac9500d5a86bb227b89f6b8502acc28","tid":157500,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"靚女 &amp; 綠帽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都系你自己揀既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227ccf86a1fccb30779675b4a241910ff3d81501","tid":157500,"uid":91107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:36:2